OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780769476
OL,3,CBuffy and Ted Lasso actor Anthony Head
OL,4,Cdies aged 72
OL,6,FAnthony Head, known for his roles in
OL,7,FTed Lasso and Buffy the Vampire
OL,8,FSlayer, has died at the age of 72.
OL,10,FThe British actor died from
OL,11,Fcomplications due to pneumonia, his
OL,12,Fdaughters Emily and Daisy Head said in
OL,13,Fa statement shared on Friday.
OL,15,F"It is with heavy hearts that we
OL,16,Fannounce the death of our
OL,17,Fextraordinary father, Anthony Head,"
OL,18,Fthey said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
