PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780769476
OL,3,CBuffy and Ted Lasso actor Anthony Head
OL,4,Cdies aged 72
OL,6,F"He passed away peacefully of
OL,7,Fcomplications due to pneumonia,
OL,8,Fsurrounded by his family. It has been,
OL,9,Fand forever will be, an honour and a
OL,10,Fprivilege to be his daughters, and to
OL,11,Fhave witnessed firsthand the impact
OL,12,Fboth he and his work have had on so
OL,13,Fmany.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
