OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780769476
OL,3,CBuffy and Ted Lasso actor Anthony Head
OL,4,Cdies aged 72
OL,6,F"We know how dearly he will be missed
OL,7,Fby friends, colleagues, and fans of
OL,8,Fthe shows he was in ` he loved his job
OL,9,Fvery much, and he always considered
OL,10,Fhimself incredibly lucky, to have been
OL,11,Fable to work alongside such
OL,12,Fexceptionally talented people, in such
OL,13,Fwonderful productions, across a career
OL,14,Fthat spanned several decades.
OL,16,F"Our grief is far greater than the
OL,17,Fhole he has left behind, but we know
OL,18,Fhis legacy will live on, in the shows
OL,19,Fhe was a part of, and in the audiences
OL,20,Fthat love them.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
