PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780769476
OL,3,CBuffy and Ted Lasso actor Anthony Head
OL,4,Cdies aged 72
OL,6,F"How lucky we are to know we are able
OL,7,Fto watch him doing what he loved, even
OL,8,Fwhen he is no longer with us.
OL,10,F"We kindly ask that our privacy is
OL,11,Frespected at this difficult time."
OL,13,FMr Head played former Richmond FC
OL,14,Fowner Rupert Mannion, the ex-husband
OL,15,Fof Hannah Waddingham's character
OL,16,FRebecca, in football comedy Ted Lasso,
OL,17,Fand librarian Rupert Giles in Buffy
OL,18,Fthe Vampire Slayer, which ran from
OL,19,F1997 to 2003.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
