CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780769476
OL,3,CBuffy and Ted Lasso actor Anthony Head
OL,4,Cdies aged 72
OL,6,FHis other notable roles include the
OL,7,FPrime Minister in Little Britain, Bill
OL,8,Fin the BBC's Motherland and Uther
OL,9,FPendragon, the father of Prince
OL,10,FArthur, in Merlin.
OL,12,FKnown for his distinctive baritone
OL,13,Fvoice, Mr Head first rose to fame in
OL,14,Fthe UK in the 1980s in the Nescafe
OL,15,FGold Blend television adverts.
OL,17,FHe was one half of the Gold Blend
OL,18,Fcouple, alongside Sharon Maughan, who
OL,19,Fbegan a slow-burning romance over a
OL,20,Fcup of coffee.
OL,26,@vD@brr
