PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780769476
OL,3,CBuffy and Ted Lasso actor Anthony Head
OL,4,Cdies aged 72
OL,6,FThe ads, which ran from 1987 to 1993,
OL,7,Fare one of the best-known examples of
OL,8,Fserialised advertising.
OL,10,FMr Head's role in Buffy made him
OL,11,Ffamous in the United States, but he
OL,12,Fleft the regular cast during the
OL,13,Fshow's sixth season, only appearing as
OL,14,Fa guest star until the series
OL,15,Fconcluded.
OL,17,FHe also acted in Manchild, Silent
OL,18,FWitness, Spooks, Doctor Who and My
OL,19,FFamily, as well as the film Repo! The
OL,20,FGenetic Opera.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
