PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1780769476
OL,3,CBuffy and Ted Lasso actor Anthony Head
OL,4,Cdies aged 72
OL,6,FIn July 2018, he joined the cast of
OL,7,FBBC Radio 4 long-running drama The
OL,8,FArchers, playing Robin Fairbrother.
OL,10,FHe was also a singer, appearing in the
OL,11,FWest End and recording music,
OL,12,Fincluding the album of the Buffy the
OL,13,FVampire Slayer musical episode, as
OL,14,Fwell as solo endeavours.
OL,16,FMr Head's long-time partner, animal
OL,17,Fwelfare campaigner Sarah Fisher, died
OL,18,Fin December 2025 aged 61.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
