OL,6,FMs Fisher was an ambassador for
OL,7,FBattersea Dogs And Cats Home and
OL,8,Fpatron of Holly Hedge Animal Sanctuary.
OL,10,FTheir daughters, Emily and Daisy, are
OL,11,Fboth actresses.
